spec_data.Name: python2-funcsigs
spec_data.Description:
funcsigs is a backport of the PEP 362 function signature features from
Python 3.3's inspect module. The backport is compatible with Python 2.6, 2.7
as well as 3.2 and up.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 01:18:42 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Python function signatures from PEP362 for Python 2.6, 2.7 and 3.2+
